title: Tech rallies early, falls late to Morehead State in Saturday showdown - Tennessee Tech
content: Tech rallies early, falls late to Morehead State in Saturday showdown  Tennessee Tech
description: COOKEVILLE, Tenn. – One comeback wasn’t enough for the Tennessee Tech baseball team Saturday afternoon, as Morehead State held off the Golden Eagles after an early rally for a 9-7 victory. The visiting Eagles claimed the Ohio Valley Conference series with the win at Quillen Field and Bush Stadium at the Averitt Express Baseball Complex.
